Komair Holdings Inc, for Cincinnati na im e buy Airline Aviation Academy, one pilot school wey dey ground for Sanford Regional Airport near Orlando, Fla.

Coma say di money don pay, but e no gree tell di price.

Coma Holdings na di parent of Comair Inc., one regional air carrier.

Airline aviation wey dey annual revenue of $5 million to $6 million don dey grow well, well because of plenty U.S. pilot wey dey near retirement age. Comair talk dis one.

De name di unit na Comair Aviation Academy and e go continue to dey go on top of di unit na Scott Williams wey be di founder.

